quiz.question: Some people might say I’m boring.
If you have a problem with me, tell me to my face.
I work well as part of a team.
I almost never pick up when my cell phone rings.
I can text, play a video game, and help my brother with his homework—at the same time.
My dream weekend? Just kicking back, with nothing at all to do.
I’d rather hang out with one friend than go to the mall with a group.
